
OpenGL shaders
==============

Technical demo of the use of shaders, VBOs, VAOs and what not.

Features
- can load obj
- script to give obj normals
- VBO/VAOs
- streaming VBO (for font)
- fonts (freetype library)
- PNG loading
- exceptions with stack trace

Library's required
- gl, glu, glew
- glfw
- png
- boost 


Compile
=======

Should compile with a recent version of GCC. Sorry, some GCC specific code
is in the exception stacktrace code.

  make


